      <details class="fq-item"><summary class="fq-q">Is shipping really free?<span class="plus">+</span></summary><div class="fq-a">Free on orders over <strong>₹999</strong>. Below that, a flat ₹49 shipping fee applies. You'll see the total before checkout.</div></details>
